name: Suprise Girl - Dolls Cleanup
description:
Suprise girl dolls cleaning house is casual games , you must help cleaning her house , everything is gonna mess.
Your task is to helping clean and tidy up all the rooms in the house.
Remember that you are given limited time, immediately complete the task before the time is over.
Each level has 3 hints that you can use, make the best use of these instructions.
Are you ready to help baby Suprise girl dolls cleaning house and restore home decorations to be even more? Let's start.
